json2yaml.com it can help us to convert jason format to yaml.


JSON PATH - WILDCARD:
Data:
{
"car": {
 "color": "blue",
 "price": "$20,000"
}
"bus": {
 "color": "white",
 "price": "$120,000"
}
}



Query:
Get car's color
$.car.color


Get bus color
$.bus.color


Get all color
$.*.color



Result:
["blue"]
["white"]

["blue", "white"]



